your kids need this book ! this book shows children that one person can make a positive impact on the world , and that god is with them even during the bad times of their lives . it was squanto 's faith in god that helped him forgive europeans for kidnapping him , and it was his faith in god that made him decide to help the pilgrims . the spiritual aspect of squanto 's life is too important to leave out when we pass this story down to our children